tags.name: relative-heading
tags.description:
`relative-heading`
`outputs the correct heading hierarchy based on parent heading`

Attributes:

  * `id` {`string`} - The relative-heading's UUID.

  * `level` {`number`} - The heading level (1-6), eg., 1 for <h1>

  * `default-level` {`number`} - The default heading level (1-6), eg., 1 for <h1>, if there  is no parent.

  * `parent-id` {`string`} - The parent relative-heading's UUID.

  * `text` {`string`} - The heading text.
